high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the right side of the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap that is in the tub.
Turn around and begin walking towards the shower, then hang right and walk up to the sink.
Place the bar of soap into the sink basin and turn the sink water on, then after a couple seconds turn the water off and pick the bar of soap back up.
Turn around and walk over to the center of the tub.
Place the bar of soap into the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bar of soap into the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Pick up the soap in the tub.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the tub.
Place the soap in the center of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bar of soap in a bathtub.

high_descs: Go to the tub behind you.
Take the soap from the tub.
Take the soap to the sink on your left.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Place the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put washed soap in the tub.
